<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.7">
<l>kāḷiyaṉ poykai kalaṅkappāyn tiṭṭavaṉ</l>
<l>nīḷmuṭi yaintilum niṉṟu naṭamceytu</l>
<l>mīḷa vavaṉuk karuḷceyta vittakaṉ</l>
<l>tōḷvali vīramē pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">tūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the heroism of the strong-armed Sage who,</l>
<l rend="indent">leaping in to disturb the pond of Kāḷiya,</l>
<l rend="indent">standing on [his] five tall heads and dancing,</l>
<l>Graced him so that [he was] liberated.</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the pure jewel hued one!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
